general.gigTitle: develop and design PHP website or web applications

sellerCard.oneLiner: Web Solutions Expert: PHP, WordPress, Data Engineer
sellerCard.description:
I am a seasoned Web Developer and Data Engineer with 5+ years of experience. I specialize in PHP (Laravel, WordPress, CodeIgniter, Core PHP), HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript, and jQuery for dynamic web solutions.

In Data Engineering, I excel in ETL/ELT, Database Design, Data Warehousing, and Big Data Processing. I work with PySpark, Hadoop, Apache Airflow, and cloud services like AWS and Azure. Proficient in SQL and Python, I deliver scalable, high-performance applications.

Let's collaborate to turn your ideas into powerful digital solutions!
